objects of enquiry which can benefit<lb/>
or enlighten the public -<lb/>
There are other uses still greater<lb/>
resulting from the communication<lb/>
of general and poplar science<lb/>
By means of it vulgar errors and<lb/>
common prejudices are constantly<lb/>
diminished-<lb/>
            <lb/>
