                rend="underline">the common knife better</hi>
            <lb/>
and at a lower rate. -<lb/>
A thousand cases of the same kind might<lb/>
be add<del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">
               <unclear>xx</unclear>
